<html lang="en">

<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8" />
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
	<title>Help - Flavors of India</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/style.css" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/help.css" />
</head>

<body>
	<nav class="navbar">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="nav">
				<img src="./images/logo.png" alt="" class="nav-logo" />
				<div class="nav-links">
					<a href="/" class="nav-link">Home</a>
					<a href="/help" class="nav-link active">Help</a>
					<a href="/menu" class="nav-link">Menu</a>
					<% if (isAuth) { %>
						<a href="/orderHistory" class="nav-link">Order History</a>
						<a href="/reservation" class="nav-link">Reservation</a>
						<%} %>
							<a href="/faq" class="nav-link">FAQ</a>
							<% if (!isAuth) { %>
								<a href="/login" class="nav-link">Login</a>
								<%} else { %>
									<a href="/api/logout" class="nav-link">Logout</a>
									<% } %>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</nav>

	<div class="container">
		<main class="main">
			<h1>Help</h1>
			<p>This page is to help users navigate the Flavors of India website.</p>
			<ul class="help-list">
				<li>
					<div class="help">The home page is where the user can see more about the restaurant and its owners.
						At the bottom, the contact us button can be clicked on if the user wishes to contact the owners
						about any question or concern they might have.</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="help">The menu page displays all the food that are available for purchase at this
						restaurant. Once selected for purchase, the user can use the text box on the right to make
						suggestions such as how spicy the food they want to be. Once the order is placed, the website
						redirects to the payment page where the user can put in information to purchase the food and
						have it either delivered/picked up at the restaurant.</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="help">The FAQ page displays frequently asked questions asked by users and clicking on
						each question displays our corresponding answer.</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="help">The reservation page can be used to make reservations and view the reservation
						history for a user by clicking the view reservations button.</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="help">The order history page is hidden if the user is not logged in to the website. Once
						the user is logged in, the order history button can be seen on the navigation bar. The user can
						view the history of their orders listed out in this page.</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<div class="help">The login/create account page is for a user to login or create an account. The
						user has to input their unique email, username, and password to create an account and state that
						they agree with the terms and conditions of the restaurant. They can view the terms and
						conditions by clicking on the link
						provided.</div>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="footer">
				<p>@2023 Flavors of India, all rights reserved Â©.</p>
			</div>
		</main>
	</div>
	<script src="./js/faq.js"></script>
</body>

</html>